Package structures.tree

Class Summary
BinarySearchTree<T extends Comparable<T>> This class implements a simple (not balanced) generic binary search tree.
BinaryTree<T> This class implements a low-level binary tree structure that can be accessed and manipulated via its nodes and its links.
Heap<T extends Comparable<T>> This class implements a generic max heap.
Visitor<T> This class implements a genericc visitor that can take some client-specific action when a binary tree node is visited.
 

Exception Summary
TreeViolationException This is a runtime exception thrown to indicate that an attempt is being made to violate the ordering of a binary tree structure.
